title: Is This a Video of Bikers on Their Way to Washington to Support Brett Kavanaugh?
subtitle: According to internet trolls, bikers everywhere in the world are supporters of President Trump and frequently rally to his support.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: A video shows the group "Bikers for Trump" on their way to Washington D.C. to support Brett Kavanaugh's confirmation hearing and demand the resignation of Sen. Feinsten.
